Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:04.96,Group,,0,0,0,,If one day you have the opportunity to meet up with my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:07.57,Group,,0,0,0,,can you tell her something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:10.36,Group,,0,0,0,,Can you tell her thank you for giving birth to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.20,0:00:12.92,Group,,0,0,0,,Tell her that because she gave birth to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:17.80,Group,,0,0,0,,I am now able to be this happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:21.08,Group,,0,0,0,,That alone was enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:32.52,Group,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:38.44,Group,,0,0,0,,Oi! Dad! Oi! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.96,0:00:42.52,Group,,0,0,0,,Dad! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:44.42,Group,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:00:59.88,Group,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.98,0:01:02.12,Group,,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,420)}Dad!\N- Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.78,0:01:04.14,Group,,0,0,0,,Oh! Everyone's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.42,0:01:06.04,Group,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, 'Everyone's here'?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.26,0:01:08.54,Group,,0,0,0,,So... how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:11.60,Group,,0,0,0,,It's a stomach ulcer! \N- Stomach ulcer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.72,0:01:14.76,Group,,0,0,0,,Yes. \N- Stomach ulcer? Is that some scary illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:18.86,Group,,0,0,0,,He'll just have to rest properly and take his medicine, then it'll heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:21.48,Group,,0,0,0,,Really? That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:25.22,Group,,0,0,0,,It's only a little hole...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.28,0:01:27.20,Group,,0,0,0,,about the size of a 1 yen coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:29.08,Group,,0,0,0,,But in order to avoid further stress...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:31.67,Group,,0,0,0,,I would recommend that you stay in hospital for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.76,0:01:34.67,Group,,0,0,0,,Huh? I don't really feel like getting on board with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.67,0:01:37.72,Group,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?\NNo matter how much you dislike hospitals...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:39.86,Group,,0,0,0,,this time you should really stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:43.10,Group,,0,0,0,,He hasn't had any proper health checks until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:45.26,Group,,0,0,0,,so please take good care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.38,0:01:48.72,Group,,0,0,0,,Really? You get stressed, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:52.74,Group,,0,0,0,,Seems so. Even though he has such a stress-free way of living.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:55.38,Group,,0,0,0,,I'd rather this 1 yen coin were 10 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:57.66,Group,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.36,0:02:03.84,Group,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that this had to happen at your wedding party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:07.32,Group,,0,0,0,,That's...\NI'm relieved, seeing your face now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:09.48,Group,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:12.44,Group,,0,0,0,,Ah, I should tell everyone at the party...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:14.26,Group,,0,0,0,,that you are fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:17.66,Group,,0,0,0,,Everyone's worried! \N- I have to tell Yuen, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:20.04,Group,,0,0,0,,Well, then your stay in hospital will continue... please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:21.44,Group,,0,0,0,,Yes!\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:24.36,Group,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:27.68,Group,,0,0,0,,Dad, come on!\N- Eh! I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:30.76,Group,,0,0,0,,Don't say "I don't want to."\N- But it's a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:33.12,Group,,0,0,0,,Did you eat something strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:43.62,Group,,0,0,0,,But for your self-indulgent son to have a stomach ulcer...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.67,0:02:45.67,Group,,0,0,0,,Yes. Even people like Ganato-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:48.68,Group,,0,0,0,,seem to have a lot on their plate when their son gets married.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:52.34,Group,,0,0,0,,Sometimes being locked away in hospital is good medicine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:02:59.56,Group,,0,0,0,,Ah... you're off to the hospital?\N- Mmh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:03.76,Group,,0,0,0,,Maybe you'll need this.\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:06.68,Group,,0,0,0,,Take care.\N- See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:18.26,Group,,0,0,0,,Ah... this is such a bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:20.70,Group,,0,0,0,,What... did even more come?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:22.44,Group,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:26.60,Group,,0,0,0,,I get that they're happy to finally meet their grandson...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:29.58,Group,,0,0,0,,but my parents send way too many presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:34.82,Group,,0,0,0,,Uwaa! More Christmas goods!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:37.90,Group,,0,0,0,,Great! Totally lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:40.66,Group,,0,0,0,,Kento-kun, Namiko-chan is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:41.96,Group,,0,0,0,,Okaaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:45.06,Group,,0,0,0,,Hello grandpa!\N- Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:47.68,Group,,0,0,0,,Dad, what about your cold?\N- Ah, it's getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.78,Group,,0,0,0,,Namiko-chan, shall we look at the books?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:52.64,Group,,0,0,0,,Ah.. ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:55.18,Group,,0,0,0,,Ah... now she's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:04:00.86,Group,,0,0,0,,That's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:03.40,Group,,0,0,0,,This one's interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.76,Group,,0,0,0,,It's mostly about sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:11.14,Group,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that Namiko is always coming around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:14.92,Group,,0,0,0,,No, everyone always looks forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:24.98,Group,,0,0,0,,Say, Kon-chan... did you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:29.24,Group,,0,0,0,,It seems like Ao recently started reading books again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:31.34,Group,,0,0,0,,Somehow... it seems like Suzumi-chan told him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:34.62,Group,,0,0,0,,that she wants him to take over "Tokyo Bandwagon" in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:35.22,Group,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:40.54,Group,,0,0,0,,Well, he still has his current job and he stayed away from books all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:44.38,Group,,0,0,0,,He seems to waver still... \NBut I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:46.38,Group,,0,0,0,,He liked books from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:50.06,Group,,0,0,0,,That's true... the rest just depends on Ao.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:54.90,Group,,0,0,0,,Ah, hello Manami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:56.34,Group,,0,0,0,,Ah, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.46,Group,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:03.82,Group,,0,0,0,,'Did something happen', you ask me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:06.78,Group,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:08.42,Group,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:16.72,Group,,0,0,0,,might have fallen in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:18.94,Group,,0,0,0,,Eh!?\N-Eh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:19.90,Group,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:22.94,Group,,0,0,0,,Love?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:31.90,Group,,0,0,0,,Should I inform your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:51.06,Group,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:54.22,Group,,0,0,0,,Ah... if you came for your father, he was released earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:56.52,Group,,0,0,0,,He told us to give his luggage to his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:58.62,Group,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:02.44,Group,,0,0,0,,Good grief... what's this... doing as he pleases...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:05.64,Group,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is it raining?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:07.68,Group,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:20.70,Group,,0,0,0,,Da...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:17.52,Group,,0,0,0,,But where did dad go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:19.34,Group,,0,0,0,,He hasn't come home for 3 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:22.62,Group,,0,0,0,,Well... isn't that what he always does?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:26.36,Group,,0,0,0,,That's right, he'll just reappear here with a Bang! suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.86,Group,,0,0,0,,But what about his recovery...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:31.24,Group,,0,0,0,,Someone sent dad a letter by air mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:33.44,Group,,0,0,0,,It's already the third one!\N- The third?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:37.66,Group,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, earlier Kayo-chan's friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:41.30,Group,,0,0,0,,said they saw your dad going for a walk with a beautiful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:45.02,Group,,0,0,0,,That Rock'n'Roller has a woman again?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:47.94,Group,,0,0,0,,"Your grandpa really likes women...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:50.64,Group,,0,0,0,,and Ao-chan certainly has these genes too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:52.66,Group,,0,0,0,,so you had better be careful."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:55.04,Group,,0,0,0,,That's what they told me.\N- Oi! Heisei playboy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:59.28,Group,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about that at all!\NDad and I are completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:02.90,Group,,0,0,0,,Hey! Leave that aside and look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:03.82,Group,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:07.90,Group,,0,0,0,,The other day you really helped us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:11.32,Group,,0,0,0,,The buy-out must have been really difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:12.42,Group,,0,0,0,,Ah... no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:16.24,Group,,0,0,0,,I'd already thought about having a publishing department and was looking for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:18.96,Group,,0,0,0,,So it was a great opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:23.86,Group,,0,0,0,,Ah... really?\NStill, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:27.88,Group,,0,0,0,,Ah... so Ma-chan has lost completely...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:30.72,Group,,0,0,0,,Say, Aiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:33.36,Group,,0,0,0,,Oh... he stood up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:43.14,Group,,0,0,0,,Would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:47.22,Group,,0,0,0,,go to E...England with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:48.00,Group,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:51.38,Group,,0,0,0,,No way!\N- Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:56.22,Group,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you saying all of a sudden, foreigner?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:57.70,Group,,0,0,0,,It's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:04.02,Group,,0,0,0,,I am going to open an exhibition in London next year...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:09.22,Group,,0,0,0,,and I would really like to exhibit Aiko-san's works there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:11.62,Group,,0,0,0,,My works...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:15.68,Group,,0,0,0,,An exhibition overseas... that's great, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:19.20,Group,,0,0,0,,That surprised me. I thought he'd suddenly propose to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:22.15,Group,,0,0,0,,But going to Maddock-san's hometown...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:24.96,Group,,0,0,0,,isn't that at least a little bit like proposing after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.84,Group,,0,0,0,,I wonder how this will end?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:28.62,Group,,0,0,0,,Stop joking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:33.12,Group,,0,0,0,,I don't care whether it's a two-person exhibition or Bishamonten!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:33.12,Info,,0,0,0,,Untranslatable Japanese pun. \NBishamonten is the god of thunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.58,0:09:36.67,Group,,0,0,0,,She won't go with you to London!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:38.78,Group,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever come here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:45.36,Group,,0,0,0,,Oi, Fujishima! What the hell are you doing here\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:47.74,Group,,0,0,0,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:50.50,Group,,0,0,0,,You're here during the day, you lazy bum!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:52.32,Group,,0,0,0,,Work properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:55.30,Group,,0,0,0,,Grandpa, he helped...\N- It's okay already, go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:10:00.04,Group,,0,0,0,,Go home! Go home! Go home!\N- You, too! Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.17,0:10:02.36,Group,,0,0,0,,Go home! Go home! \N- I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:04.40,Group,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since Kanichi yelled at them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:06.24,Group,,0,0,0,,Well... but this is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:09.36,Group,,0,0,0,,These two are good people though...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:13.44,Group,,0,0,0,,Well, but since you're still young
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:16.67,Group,,0,0,0,,you might as well give Kanichi one or two great-grandchildren.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:18.80,Group,,0,0,0,,Great-grandchildren!? \N - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.94,0:10:21.48,Group,,0,0,0,,But if it's about that, Ao and Suzumi-chan are next!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:25.04,Group,,0,0,0,,What?\N- Grandchildren? No way, uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:28.16,Group,,0,0,0,,Manami-san is talking about love, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:30.54,Group,,0,0,0,,Seems like this has become our hot topic recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:31.92,Group,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:34.58,Group,,0,0,0,,What? What?\NManami-san is in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:36.80,Group,,0,0,0,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.36,Group,,0,0,0,,Ah! Hello! Please come in!\N- Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:42.64,Group,,0,0,0,,{\pos(426,426)}Well, it seems like they haven't come home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:42.84,Group,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:47.28,Group,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask you about Namiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:53.84,Group,,0,0,0,,Did she maybe say weird things recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:56.14,Group,,0,0,0,,"Weird things"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:11:01.06,Group,,0,0,0,,Recently she makes up really strange lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:03.20,Group,,0,0,0,,A sheep...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:07.38,Group,,0,0,0,,A sheep appeared and followed her. It bothered her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:10.24,Group,,0,0,0,,A sheep?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:15.36,Group,,0,0,0,,But she says as soon as she arrives at "Tokyo Bandwagon", it just disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:19.14,Group,,0,0,0,,So she wants to be here all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:24.80,Group,,0,0,0,,The sheep appears and then... disappears...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.40,Group,,0,0,0,,Namiko-chan said something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:32.84,Group,,0,0,0,,Yes. But that's a weird kind of lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:36.18,Group,,0,0,0,,But it might also be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:40.70,Group,,0,0,0,,Not many sheep around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:44.88,Group,,0,0,0,,{\pos(432,416)}Well, if it was a raccoon or a wild boar, that would be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:46.22,Group,,0,0,0,,And she said it's this big!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:49.62,Group,,0,0,0,,And even though it's a sheep it walks on two legs like a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:52.67,Group,,0,0,0,,Well, but...\N- Uwaaah! It's Sheepman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:55.42,Group,,0,0,0,,Total surprise! \N- Kento! Don't stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:58.98,Group,,0,0,0,,Sorry!\N- But she seemed deadly serious when she said...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:01.94,Group,,0,0,0,,that since a sheep followed her she didn't want to go anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:04.30,Group,,0,0,0,,And only if she comes here, the sheep disappears...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:07.14,Group,,0,0,0,,and then she can go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.00,Group,,0,0,0,,She might really have seen something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:14.04,Group,,0,0,0,,Okay! I will research that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:17.54,Group,,0,0,0,,Whether Sheepman really appears around Namiko-chan is around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:21.04,Group,,0,0,0,,I said don't stand up!\N- I am very sorryyyy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:24.90,Group,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll help you! \NKon-chan, can we borrow your camera tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:26.78,Group,,0,0,0,,Sure. I'm trusting you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:30.10,Group,,0,0,0,,That's nice...\NSomehow acting like detectives seems like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:33.12,Group,,0,0,0,,Is Aiko still at Haru's?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:35.74,Group,,0,0,0,,Yes. Ko-san took holidays from yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:38.22,Group,,0,0,0,,and it seems like Manami-san is still down because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:40.54,Group,,0,0,0,,So Ko-san is taking a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:42.46,Group,,0,0,0,,Ah... right! Manami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.76,Group,,0,0,0,,Huh? Manami-san's in love?\N- Ami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:48.42,Group,,0,0,0,,You've become better at this!\N- Huh? You noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:51.98,Group,,0,0,0,,I did! It's superb!\N- Could it be that... I'm the only one who doesn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.94,Group,,0,0,0,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:01.40,Group,,0,0,0,,Just because my feelings were exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:05.18,Group,,0,0,0,,That seemed to be a heavy burden for Ko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:08.48,Group,,0,0,0,,He won't answer his phone, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:12.24,Group,,0,0,0,,Did you actually do something that exposed your feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:14.06,Group,,0,0,0,,I don't remember doing so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:22.36,Group,,0,0,0,,I thought he should have the shop's footwear, so I bought us matching sandals...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:26.26,Group,,0,0,0,,and I may have drawn a little heart on the shopping list....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:28.66,Group,,0,0,0,,Well... that gives you away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.18,Group,,0,0,0,,Ao... you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:34.74,Group,,0,0,0,,What should I do? The way things are he might quit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.42,0:13:37.84,Group,,0,0,0,,When Ganato-san introduced him to me, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:42.52,Group,,0,0,0,,Well, if you like him, he can't be that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:45.40,Group,,0,0,0,,That's true. I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:04.28,Group,,0,0,0,,Da...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.71,0:14:09.60,Group,,0,0,0,,Dad! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:13.50,Group,,0,0,0,,Dad! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:35.14,Group,,0,0,0,,Your father didn't come home yesterday either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.64,Group,,0,0,0,,Should I go to the hospital again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:46.40,Group,,0,0,0,,Well... just for one reason or other...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:53.86,Group,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:02.24,Group,,0,0,0,,I'll should go for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:06.96,Group,,0,0,0,,Ah... wait. Here, Ao-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:11.04,Group,,0,0,0,,That's the book I recommend recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:13.34,Group,,0,0,0,,Please read it on your walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:14.66,Group,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:16.60,Group,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:18.14,Group,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:28.32,Group,,0,0,0,,He does love his dad after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.16,Group,,0,0,0,,Ko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:42.50,Group,,0,0,0,,Ko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:45.26,Group,,0,0,0,,Ah... hello
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:50.56,Group,,0,0,0,,Manami-san is worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:53.10,Group,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:59.42,Group,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you moving home?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:02.36,Group,,0,0,0,,Ah... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:05.02,Group,,0,0,0,,But Ko-san... earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:07.70,Group,,0,0,0,,you said you were happy to be able to work at Haru's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:21.58,Group,,0,0,0,,A lot has happened in my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:25.88,Group,,0,0,0,,And if possible I wanted to be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:27.78,Group,,0,0,0,,not to get too close to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:30.16,Group,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:35.60,Group,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:38.04,Group,,0,0,0,,that you like Manami-san, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:41.00,Group,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:45.74,Group,,0,0,0,,I'm a man who is not fit to fall in love with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:56.18,Group,,0,0,0,,For a long time I worked at a traditional Japanese restaurant in Karuizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:16:58.70,Group,,0,0,0,,There are nice ones here, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:17:00.78,Group,,0,0,0,,The head chef there favoured me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:05.60,Group,,0,0,0,,and let me marry his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:09.74,Group,,0,0,0,,We were just scraping along...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:12.30,Group,,0,0,0,,but we lived happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:13.62,Group,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:15.88,Group,,0,0,0,,But my wife was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:18.52,Group,,0,0,0,,with a chronic disease of the lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:25.52,Group,,0,0,0,,She died when she was only 27 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:35.02,Group,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for making you remember something that painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:36.44,Group,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.67,0:17:42.92,Group,,0,0,0,,After that, I hurt someone I care about...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.32,Group,,0,0,0,,with the same hand I use to prepare food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:18:00.34,Group,,0,0,0,,I plan to leave this town next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:04.16,Group,,0,0,0,,Please let me visit you again before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:09.00,Group,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:20.40,Group,,0,0,0,,Whatever happened... there's nobody who can make somebody else happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:29.02,Group,,0,0,0,,But I'm already...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:32.58,Group,,0,0,0,,We are having a party at our house next week on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:38.78,Group,,0,0,0,,If it's okay, please come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:57.42,Group,,0,0,0,,Yes, understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:02.82,Group,,0,0,0,,If there's something else, please...\N- Say, is that a  call about work?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:06.88,Group,,0,0,0,,Yes, maybe. Somehow he's researchingsomething all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:09.96,Group,,0,0,0,,We're hooome!\N- Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:12.66,Group,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!\NIt was cold outside today, mmh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:16.86,Group,,0,0,0,,It's okay, it's okay. Namiko-chan, should I show you the books? Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:18.90,Group,,0,0,0,,Yes! Excuse meee!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:22.28,Group,,0,0,0,,Just go ahead. \N- Well then, I'll prepare something for afternoon tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:31.64,Group,,0,0,0,,Say... how did it go?\N- Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:34.98,Group,,0,0,0,,I took the picture! Of Sheepman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:35.98,Group,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:39.96,Group,,0,0,0,,Oh!\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.56,0:19:42.92,Group,,0,0,0,,What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:49.52,Group,,0,0,0,,Delicious!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:53.26,Group,,0,0,0,,This is impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:56.78,Group,,0,0,0,,Aren't the people around who see this surprised, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:58.30,Group,,0,0,0,,Right.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:01.28,Group,,0,0,0,,Someone does this especially for whatever reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:05.14,Group,,0,0,0,,Well, but that confirms...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:08.30,Group,,0,0,0,,that Namiko-chan wasn't spinning wild ideas but telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:11.18,Group,,0,0,0,,So that means he followed Namiko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:15.84,Group,,0,0,0,,Yeah... so this sheepman follows Namiko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:18.28,Group,,0,0,0,,but disappears when she comes to our house?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.62,0:20:22.14,Group,,0,0,0,,For just a pervert, this is quite complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:27.42,Group,,0,0,0,,This sheepman has to have some goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:39.24,Group,,0,0,0,,Sheep...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:41.22,Group,,0,0,0,,We thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:44.11,Group,,0,0,0,,she made it up because she missed Kento-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:46.00,Group,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:50.24,Group,,0,0,0,,Ah! Dad! Mum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:54.56,Group,,0,0,0,,Namiko, I'm sorry. You must've been scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:57.82,Group,,0,0,0,,That's true... when he's just following you for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:01.26,Group,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.02,0:21:08.06,Group,,0,0,0,,Truth is, Sheep-san is really kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:12.36,Group,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:15.82,Group,,0,0,0,,What's wrong Suzumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:36.02,Group,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:43.40,Group,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:49.00,Group,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:50.94,Group,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.74,0:21:55.13,Group,,0,0,0,,Eh? Your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.66,0:22:03.44,Group,,0,0,0,,Oi! Grandpa! Grandpa!\N- Aaah! Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:05.92,Group,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Grandpa!\N- Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.44,0:22:09.90,Group,,0,0,0,,This is pretty uncomfortable...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:14.56,Group,,0,0,0,,Well, the other day... ah...ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:19.72,Group,,0,0,0,,When I went home from the hospital, Namiko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:23.72,Group,,0,0,0,,Well, when I went to the shrine to pray I suddenly heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.52,0:22:30.48,Group,,0,0,0,,She said "I don't want dad and mum to divorce."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.00,0:22:37.02,Group,,0,0,0,,and "I always want to play with Kento-kun!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:41.06,Group,,0,0,0,,I got worried when I listened to what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:43.62,Group,,0,0,0,,It seems like the two fought every night...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.60,0:22:46.68,Group,,0,0,0,,and that she had to change schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.66,0:22:50.96,Group,,0,0,0,,Namiko-chan and I thought about what's best to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.48,0:22:53.72,Group,,0,0,0,,And then Namiko-chan said...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.30,0:22:56.62,Group,,0,0,0,,well, what if she was pursued by some unspeakable monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:22:59.10,Group,,0,0,0,,and only Kento could save her...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.20,0:23:01.58,Group,,0,0,0,,wouldn't that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.22,0:23:05.92,Group,,0,0,0,,Eh? Me?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.88,0:23:10.92,Group,,0,0,0,,And then she wouldn't need to change schools and could be with Kento forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.24,0:23:14.40,Group,,0,0,0,,So I thought well, let's think about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.24,0:23:21.46,Group,,0,0,0,,And then this unspeakable thing was this sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.66,0:23:26.00,Group,,0,0,0,,Well... Namiko-chan requested the sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.82,0:23:30.04,Group,,0,0,0,,And Jun-chan, that make-up artist...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:34.78,Group,,0,0,0,,he let me stay over at his place and applied the make-up for 3 hours every day for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:40.66,Group,,0,0,0,,Namiko, you know... we haven't thought about getting divorced at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.20,0:23:43.46,Group,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N- Eh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.62,0:23:48.86,Group,,0,0,0,,That's true. My husband just suddenly told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:51.04,Group,,0,0,0,,that this company is transferring him to homeplace Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.32,0:23:54.64,Group,,0,0,0,,I asked him why and then we ended up fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.14,0:23:57.46,Group,,0,0,0,,She must've misunderstood...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:23:59.94,Group,,0,0,0,,Hokkaido?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.24,0:24:04.96,Group,,0,0,0,,We thought that Namiko hadn't noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.72,0:24:10.40,Group,,0,0,0,,Children see a lot you don't realise.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.04,0:24:14.03,Group,,0,0,0,,Namiko is really clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.50,0:24:18.38,Group,,0,0,0,,Namiko, we're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.32,0:24:22.64,Group,,0,0,0,,Everyone... we're really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.86,0:24:28.28,Group,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is.\NWell, I can't tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.36,0:24:30.16,Group,,0,0,0,,what's the best thing to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.24,0:24:34.54,Group,,0,0,0,,but everyone including Namiko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.88,0:24:37.06,Group,,0,0,0,,can think this through, mmh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.08,0:24:40.22,Group,,0,0,0,,Yes... you worried so much about us...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.88,0:24:46.25,Group,,0,0,0,,you even applied such complicated make-up\Nand you kept Namiko company. 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.90,0:24:48.44,Group,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.68,0:24:50.72,Group,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.04,0:24:57.04,Group,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Namiko-chan. They found me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.34,0:25:00.54,Group,,0,0,0,,Thank you, kind sheep-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.02,0:25:10.04,Group,,0,0,0,,Namiko-chan... don't forget this LOVE, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.96,0:25:17.98,Group,,0,0,0,,And even if you are separated at some point...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.38,0:25:23.54,Group,,0,0,0,,when you become an adult, this genuine LOVE...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.74,0:25:28.24,Group,,0,0,0,,will be the most important treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.52,0:25:30.04,Group,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.80,0:25:43.36,Group,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.60,0:25:46.88,Group,,0,0,0,,Where are you going now?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.86,0:25:50.88,Group,,0,0,0,,Well... look, I'll have to give this back to Jun-chan quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.92,0:25:55.66,Group,,0,0,0,,Why did you go to that shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.00,0:26:01.30,Group,,0,0,0,,Aren't you hiding something from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.26,0:26:04.80,Group,,0,0,0,,Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.52,0:26:11.02,Group,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it would be better if you lived more selfishly?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.74,0:26:13.26,Group,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.28,0:26:17.80,Group,,0,0,0,,This store is important to you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.38,0:26:23.03,Group,,0,0,0,,But it's also okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.80,0:26:25.92,Group,,0,0,0,,for you not to think about taking over the store at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.76,0:26:29.92,Group,,0,0,0,,Live as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.18,0:26:33.84,Group,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.70,0:26:35.94,Group,,0,0,0,,Just live as you think is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.38,0:26:53.34,Group,,0,0,0,,A week has passed since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.90,0:26:57.22,Group,,0,0,0,,and today is Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.68,0:27:01.72,Group,,0,0,0,,I decided to take up the new post and leave my family here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.64,0:27:05.80,Group,,0,0,0,,And dad offered to move in with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.20,0:27:07.98,Group,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.08,0:27:09.54,Group,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.36,0:27:14.53,Group,,0,0,0,,I'm also worried about leaving these two behind and going to Hokkaido...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.14,0:27:16.94,Group,,0,0,0,,but if my father-in-law is there, I feel easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.14,0:27:19.44,Group,,0,0,0,,Honestly speaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.22,0:27:23.50,Group,,0,0,0,,I'm still not feeling that certain about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.92,0:27:26.90,Group,,0,0,0,,but by spending the time together...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.02,0:27:30.05,Group,,0,0,0,,we can catch up on the time we lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.88,0:27:33.38,Group,,0,0,0,,So we can become a real family again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.30,0:27:38.30,Group,,0,0,0,,Oi! Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.58,0:27:40.76,Group,,0,0,0,,You should be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.12,0:27:46.16,Group,,0,0,0,,Yes... all of this is just thanks to you and Ganato-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.66,0:27:50.05,Group,,0,0,0,,So from now on we can play together forever, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.16,0:27:50.72,Group,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.04,0:27:55.28,Group,,0,0,0,,And don't forget I'll come home once a month, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.36,0:27:57.78,Group,,0,0,0,,Thank you, dad. And grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.28,0:28:00.84,Group,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.44,0:28:04.07,Group,,0,0,0,,That's great
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.72,0:28:06.46,Group,,0,0,0,,{\pos(422,426)}Hello!\N- Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.12,0:28:07.96,Group,,0,0,0,,Wai...wai...sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.15,0:28:12.10,Group,,0,0,0,,Ah... hello!\N- You two brought a lot of stuff with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.18,0:28:14.68,Group,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not much, but I brought some Christmas presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.76,0:28:18.56,Group,,0,0,0,,I came to prepare the food for the Christmas party.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.80,0:28:20.74,Group,,0,0,0,,It's traditional English food, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.20,0:28:25.07,Group,,0,0,0,,With Fujishima-san and Maddock-san invited...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.68,0:28:30.52,Group,,0,0,0,,this Christmas will become pretty lively, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.36,0:28:34.10,Group,,0,0,0,,Everyone who's free right now...\Nlet's have a drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.10,0:28:37.96,Group,,0,0,0,,We have some good Japanese sake.\N- That's nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.98,0:28:40.06,Group,,0,0,0,,I want to drink, too!\N- That's nothing for kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.88,0:28:42.07,Group,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.96,0:28:46.90,Group,,0,0,0,,Yo! Ko-san! Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.76,0:28:52.55,Group,,0,0,0,,Ganato-san, you seem quite healthy. What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.80,0:28:53.14,Group,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.68,0:29:01.20,Group,,0,0,0,,I came to say hello to you one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.72,0:29:06.44,Group,,0,0,0,,Ko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.80,0:29:14.80,Group,,0,0,0,,Ao-san, what you said the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.54,0:29:16.92,Group,,0,0,0,,really moved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.28,0:29:21.24,Group,,0,0,0,,But indeed I...\N- I heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.04,0:29:26.24,Group,,0,0,0,,That back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.34,0:29:32.92,Group,,0,0,0,,you injured your master's right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.26,0:29:34.68,Group,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.08,0:29:39.30,Group,,0,0,0,,Ko-san, it's not your fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.00,0:29:41.60,Group,,0,0,0,,that your wife died.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.68,0:29:44.78,Group,,0,0,0,,You kept telling yourself you should have been able to do more...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.96,0:29:48.05,Group,,0,0,0,,and you constantly blamed yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.56,0:29:54.42,Group,,0,0,0,,And then finally that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.44,0:29:58.06,Group,,0,0,0,,you wanted to follow your wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.92,0:30:03.08,Group,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.58,0:30:05.90,Group,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.64,0:30:08.24,Group,,0,0,0,,Please let me die already...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.04,0:30:18.32,Group,,0,0,0,,That's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.32,0:30:24.30,Group,,0,0,0,,The injury was so bad that he had to undergo surgery immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.66,0:30:27.30,Group,,0,0,0,,I left the store at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.76,0:30:31.08,Group,,0,0,0,,I left Karuizawa and worked at bars and izakayas...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.22,0:30:35.08,Group,,0,0,0,,and decided never to work as a cook again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.30,0:30:40.26,Group,,0,0,0,,One night I met Ganato-san in this town...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.48,0:30:44.28,Group,,0,0,0,,and he told me I should start a new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.28,0:30:51.57,Group,,0,0,0,,So then you came to Haru's.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.00,0:30:52.54,Group,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.60,0:30:56.98,Group,,0,0,0,,Haru's is a great store...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.50,0:31:03.55,Group,,0,0,0,,and I thought staying there for the rest of my life would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.22,0:31:07.56,Group,,0,0,0,,But you can't accept Manami-san's feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.84,0:31:13.92,Group,,0,0,0,,I'm a man who hurt someone he was grateful to...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.64,0:31:16.70,Group,,0,0,0,,and then tried to take his own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.96,0:31:19.96,Group,,0,0,0,,I can't make Manami-san happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.50,0:31:21.46,Group,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.70,0:31:27.03,Group,,0,0,0,,I can't stay with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.22,0:31:36.55,Group,,0,0,0,,The food will be ready soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.76,0:31:39.16,Group,,0,0,0,,Until then, maybe you'd like to try some of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.20,0:31:43.05,Group,,0,0,0,,That's very well prepared. It looks like from a store!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.08,0:31:46.55,Group,,0,0,0,,Yeah... this too, please try this if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.78,0:31:54.54,Group,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.74,0:31:57.86,Group,,0,0,0,,Shougouin-style simmered white turnip?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.18,0:32:04.30,Group,,0,0,0,,Please go ahead, Ko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.92,0:32:06.74,Group,,0,0,0,,Could you please try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.56,0:32:41.92,Group,,0,0,0,,This food... it was prepared by...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.90,0:32:50.90,Group,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Ko.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.46,0:32:53.34,Group,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.10,0:33:02.05,Group,,0,0,0,,How is it? Did I become worse at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.60,0:33:03.12,Group,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.34,0:33:05.32,Group,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.48,0:33:09.30,Group,,0,0,0,,As soon as I saw the way it was prepared, I thought this could only be...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.94,0:33:15.24,Group,,0,0,0,,and the way it's cut... and the way it's seasoned...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.36,0:33:17.28,Group,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.14,0:33:22.76,Group,,0,0,0,,Quite some time has passed... but it's still just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.52,0:33:33.34,Group,,0,0,0,,I'm working in Kyoto right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.40,0:33:36.66,Group,,0,0,0,,"Since you still seem like you're worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.14,0:33:41.16,Group,,0,0,0,,can you not give him a pep talk?"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.54,0:33:43.57,Group,,0,0,0,,Ao specially came to ask me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.10,0:33:44.68,Group,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.68,0:33:47.52,Group,,0,0,0,,Say, Ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.28,0:33:49.96,Group,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.76,0:34:00.96,Group,,0,0,0,,Even though you had no proper place here...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.32,0:34:05.02,Group,,0,0,0,,you were able to meet amazing people...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.02,0:34:11.02,Group,,0,0,0,,who worry about you from the bottom of their heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.12,0:34:12.48,Group,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.84,0:34:17.84,Group,,0,0,0,,I don't hold a grudge against you about my daughter either.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.36,0:34:24.58,Group,,0,0,0,,You should walk a new path... facing forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.76,0:34:27.24,Group,,0,0,0,,That's all I wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.96,0:34:30.86,Group,,0,0,0,,Right, Ko.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.90,0:34:32.88,Group,,0,0,0,,YOU, make that kind of food too!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.18,0:34:39.86,Group,,0,0,0,,From now, for the sake of these people...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.24,0:34:43.38,Group,,0,0,0,,you should show off your skills to your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.76,0:35:00.62,Group,,0,0,0,,Master... Ao-san... thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.64,0:35:06.40,Group,,0,0,0,,Ko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.08,0:35:13.55,Group,,0,0,0,,I think there's still a lot you have to talk to Hisamoto-san about.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.94,0:35:15.32,Group,,0,0,0,,But first of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.82,0:35:18.56,Group,,0,0,0,,maybe you should get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.88,0:35:22.94,Group,,0,0,0,,Eh? 'Going'?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.60,0:35:27.38,Group,,0,0,0,,To Haru's. Manami-san is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.54,0:35:31.42,Group,,0,0,0,,Yes, she's all alone on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.94,0:35:38.05,Group,,0,0,0,,Manami-san is waiting all alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.78,0:35:42.90,Group,,0,0,0,,Heee.. really!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.26,0:35:45.24,Group,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.44,0:35:50.44,Group,,0,0,0,,Ko-san, you have to accept the LOVE.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.94,0:35:52.84,Group,,0,0,0,,Today's the Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.62,0:35:56.70,Group,,0,0,0,,You just have to accept Manami-san's LOVE!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.10,0:35:58.06,Group,,0,0,0,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.48,0:36:12.46,Group,,0,0,0,,From tomorrow onwards I'll be in the store again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.22,0:36:17.06,Group,,0,0,0,,So please... come over!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.56,0:36:20.92,Group,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.44,0:36:30.30,Group,,0,0,0,,What a relief! Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.30,0:36:35.12,Group,,0,0,0,,Ao! What a smart moooove!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.58,0:36:38.50,Group,,0,0,0,,Hisamoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.66,0:36:42.68,Group,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.38,0:36:46.40,Group,,0,0,0,,No... thank {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.66,0:36:49.96,Group,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.18,0:36:51.80,Group,,0,0,0,,Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.44,0:36:54.42,Group,,0,0,0,,That's LOVE!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.90,0:37:00.80,Group,,0,0,0,,What's LOVE...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.04,0:37:47.90,Group,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.24,0:37:55.08,Group,,0,0,0,,Manami-san, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.92,0:38:03.92,Group,,0,0,0,,{\pos(418,428)}Merry Christmas!\N- Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.50,0:38:05.66,Group,,0,0,0,,How many times did we toast already?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.72,0:38:08.04,Group,,0,0,0,,It's completely different! Me...merry...\N- Nice pronunciation!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.12,0:38:11.02,Group,,0,0,0,,Maddock-san's mince pie is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.04,0:38:14.06,Group,,0,0,0,,But the one my mum in London makes is much more delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.10,0:38:16.46,Group,,0,0,0,,I want to try this!\NThis original pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.14,0:38:19.32,Group,,0,0,0,,Mum, what will you do about the exhibition?\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.50,0:38:23.94,Group,,0,0,0,,Ah... but... I find it really hard to believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.00,0:38:26.62,Group,,0,0,0,,that my pictures are valuable enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.88,0:38:29.94,Group,,0,0,0,,to be exhibited overseas like that.\N- That's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.98,0:38:32.18,Group,,0,0,0,,My friend came to the cafe earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.44,0:38:35.60,Group,,0,0,0,,and when he saw your pictures he said they were great.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.64,0:38:37.28,Group,,0,0,0,,Tha...thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.38,0:38:40.08,Group,,0,0,0,,I agree completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.10,0:38:42.34,Group,,0,0,0,,I too think that Aiko-san's pictures are so valuable that more people should see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.28,0:38:44.86,Group,,0,0,0,,If Fujishima-san says this, it might be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.06,0:38:48.12,Group,,0,0,0,,You have quite a collection of foreign art, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.46,0:38:50.72,Group,,0,0,0,,Is that a hobby of yours?\N- Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.42,0:38:54.94,Group,,0,0,0,,Well... but that's great, isn't it? \NA two-person exhibition in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.08,0:38:59.24,Group,,0,0,0,,I will accompany you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.42,0:39:00.16,Group,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.44,0:39:04.74,Group,,0,0,0,,Ah... actually, why don't all of you come along too?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.80,0:39:07.48,Group,,0,0,0,,No way! I want to go!\N- Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.55,0:39:09.34,Group,,0,0,0,,NO, NO, NO, NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.26,0:39:13.42,Group,,0,0,0,,Aiko, what do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.50,0:39:16.64,Group,,0,0,0,,Well... being told to decide on the spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.78,0:39:19.26,Group,,0,0,0,,That's true! This is an important decision...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.34,0:39:21.64,Group,,0,0,0,,Yes. Ai-chan, you'd better take your time thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.10,0:39:22.56,Group,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.20,0:39:29.90,Group,,0,0,0,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.94,0:39:33.54,Group,,0,0,0,,That's the way LOVE...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.32,0:39:36.10,Group,,0,0,0,,always flows in this family.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.14,0:39:39.16,Group,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.84,0:39:41.78,Group,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.68,0:39:44.38,Group,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.40,0:39:48.54,Group,,0,0,0,,have cancer of the voice box.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.64,0:39:59.78,Group,,0,0,0,,If I get surgery...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.20,0:40:04.00,Group,,0,0,0,,my voice might vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.94,0:40:07.80,Group,,0,0,0,,I might not be able to sing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.38,0:40:10.66,Group,,0,0,0,,The Rock'n'Roll...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.88,0:40:13.63,Group,,0,0,0,,might disappear, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.54,0:40:18.42,Group,,0,0,0,,Dying is not LOVE.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.86,0:40:23.54,Group,,0,0,0,,But not being able to sing anymore isn't LOVE either.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.92,0:40:28.74,Group,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.30,0:40:31.80,Group,,0,0,0,,until I'm on the verge of dying...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.22,0:40:39.50,Group,,0,0,0,,I want to sing the LOVE.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.10,0:40:47.86,Group,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.20,0:40:54.20,Group,,0,0,0,,I decided not to have surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.68,0:41:07.36,Group,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.98,0:41:11.40,Group,,0,0,0,,my last Christmas song for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.76,0:41:39.72,Group,,0,0,0,,♪～ きよし
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.48,0:41:45.78,Group,,0,0,0,,♪～ このよる
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.76,0:41:59.20,Group,,0,0,0,,♪～ ほしは ひかり
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.12,0:42:10.98,Group,,0,0,0,,♪～ すくいのみこは
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.96,0:42:22.58,Group,,0,0,0,,♪～ みははのむねに
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.84,0:42:35.14,Group,,0,0,0,,♪～ ねむりたもう
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.74,0:42:44.60,Group,,0,0,0,,♪～ ゆめやすく
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.26,0:42:58.24,Group,,0,0,0,,♪～ ねむりたもう
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.22,0:43:10.06,Group,,0,0,0,,♪～ ゆめやすく
